				We have configured our payment options in such a way that any customers can pay for their gift in Bangladesh regardless their currency, their current location and availability of payment facilities. First you have to place your order and then you have to select a payment method out of following available options -<br /><br/><h3>Pay by Credit Card:</h3><u>Card issued in Bangladesh: </u>You will be able to pay online in&nbsp;BDT (টাকা) using your AMEX, VISA, MASTER card issued by <u>any bank in Bangladesh</u> (BRAC, SCB, UCB, Eastern Bank, Dutch Bangla Bank (DBBL), Trust Bank, Prime Bank, Mercantile Bank, Jamuna Bank, Mutual Trust Bank, Premier Bank, City Bank, Southeast Bank etc.). Our 100% secure online payment processing gateway is managed by CityBank and <a href="#" title="Upohar">BRAC bank</a>. Your order will be confirmed instantly if the payment is successful. You may need to contact your bank to enable your card for online transaction. <br /><br/>
